    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the hall with the peaked roof. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho cūḷakokanadā pajjunnassa dhītā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ mahāvanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. ",
          "en": "Then, late at night, the beautiful Kokanadā the Younger, Pajjunna’s daughter, lighting up the entire Great Wood, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:1.4",
          "pli": "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā cūḷakokanadā pajjunnassa dhītā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
          "en": "and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:2.1",
          "pli": "“Idhāgamā vijjupabhāsavaṇṇā, ",
          "en": "“Kokanadā, Pajjunna’s daughter, came here, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:2.2",
          "pli": "Kokanadā pajjunnassa dhītā; ",
          "en": "beautiful as a flash of lightning. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:2.3",
          "pli": "Buddhañca dhammañca namassamānā, ",
          "en": "Revering the Buddha and the teaching, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:2.4",
          "pli": "Gāthācimā atthavatī abhāsi. ",
          "en": "she spoke these verses full of meaning. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:3.1",
          "pli": "Bahunāpi kho taṃ vibhajeyyaṃ, ",
          "en": "The teaching is such that "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:3.2",
          "pli": "Pariyāyena tādiso dhammo; ",
          "en": "I could analyze it in many different ways. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:3.3",
          "pli": "Saṃkhittamatthaṃ lapayissāmi, ",
          "en": "However, I will state the meaning in brief "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:3.4",
          "pli": "Yāvatā me manasā pariyattaṃ. ",
          "en": "as far as I have learned it by heart. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:4.1",
          "pli": "Pāpaṃ na kayirā vacasā manasā, ",
          "en": "You should never do anything bad "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:4.2",
          "pli": "Kāyena vā kiñcana sabbaloke; ",
          "en": "by speech or mind or body in all the world. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:4.3",
          "pli": "Kāme pahāya satimā sampajāno, ",
          "en": "Having given up sensual pleasures, mindful and aware, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:4.4",
          "pli": "Dukkhaṃ na sevetha anatthasaṃhitan”ti. ",
          "en": "you shouldn’t keep doing what’s painful and pointless.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:4.5",
          "pli": "Satullapakāyikavaggo catuttho. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:5.1",
          "pli": "Sabbhimaccharinā sādhu, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:5.2",
          "pli": "na santujjhānasaññino; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:5.3",
          "pli": "Saddhā samayo sakalikaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.40:5.4",
          "pli": "ubho pajjunnadhītaroti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
